OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Seven students are suing a Texas school
OL,6, district over its dress-code policy    
OL,7, banning boys from having long hair.    
OL,9,FAccording to the suit, school officials
OL,10,Fsuspended a 9-year-old boy for a month,
OL,11,Fbarred him from recess and normal lunch
OL,12,Fbreaks as punishment for long hair.    
OL,14,FHe and the other students, aged 7 to   
OL,15,F17, say the policy violates the        
OL,16,Fconstitution and Title IX - a  federal 
OL,17,Flaw prohibiting sex discrimination.    
OL,19,FThe school district said on Thursday it
OL,20,Fwas reviewing the suit.                
